<br>
So you cast it on a mob, and you have a dual wielding double attcking warrior hittting it. The warrior is successful on all 4 attack attempts, thus he is healed for 24 to 36 points, depending on what level of Mark spell you have.<br>
<br>
Personally, i think the healing part is trivial, the important part is the fact that it strips the damage shields. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em> In Perfect Hate, and Perfect Faith</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
